items.name: LORA Cute Pony
items.description:
LORA Cute Pony
A Pony themed LORA for getting more consistent good pony images. Generally SAFE and is trained on only safe images.
Not good for replicating the mane six, better for one offs. Style is a bit vector but more closer to fan art without being 3D or Drawn looking.

Recommended Models
PonyMaker V1 – best for pony parts and derpi tags
Icedcoffemix V1 – more detail and options but less pony
I suggest starting with PonyMaker then Txt2Img with PonyMaker or Icedcoffemix. BUT starting with Icedcoffemix will give you more freedom but less “pony accuracy”.

With PonyMaker
The default Bias is towards white body, pink hair but you can easily force common colors. Prefers derpi based tags.
Key Tags – included in samples / similar to PonyMaker
All samples are RAW Txt2Img+Img2Img no inpaint or editing.

My tests and best results were with -
0.6-0.7 weight <lora:70_CutePony:0.6>, Steps: 24, Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras, CFG scale: 8, Size: 624x512, Denoising strength: 0.55, Clip skip:2, Hires upscale: 1.5, Hires steps: 12

<lora:70_CutePony:0.6> , Derpibooru_p_95, feral pony, (small:1.2), (cute:1.2), tail, fur, hooves, (small body:1.2), safe, XXX skin, XXX XXX hair, XXXXX pony, standing, XXX eyes,
from below, XXXXXXXX background, (vector:0.8) (detailed:0.6)

(derpibooru_p_low:1.1), SFM, bad anatomy, (anthro:1.1), (human:1.1), compression artifacts, ugly, poor quality, blank eye, (deformed:1.3), (contortion:1.0), (missing limbs:1.0), (extra limbs:1.1), (deformed limbs:0.8), (blurry:0.8), (watermark:0.6), (lowres:0.8), CCTV surveillance, human hands, fingers

items.name: BBB - SDXL
items.description:
BBB in Version 2.0.
No Refiner needed.

This model will help you create voluptuous bodies.

I have taken your criticism to heart and refined version 1 with over 1500+ images, which have ensured that the oversized breasts have been tamed and that more control is possible. The model has also become more versatile.

The model was trained using only photos, but is also capable of representing other things and styles.

Good resolutions are:

800x1200

960x1280

1024x1024

The model also feels comfortable in even slightly higher resolutions. At 960x1440, proportions are often getting looser, though.

Breasts can still be shown large if desired. For this you can well use the prompt (big breasts:1-3), where 3 completely messes up the space-time-continuum. Often it is helpful to add "nude" as a negative prompt, if the lady should not be naked.

There are still a few kinks that need to be worked out of the model. Feel free to give me your feedback. I am happy about every suggestion. Version 3 will be realized with your help.

I'm excited to see what you conjure up with BBB.

items.name: Desi Coffee - SDXL LoKR - Tiny Sized LoRA for Indian faces/ skin tones (Experimental)
items.description:
This LoKR is designed to generate Indian/ South Asian looking faces and skin-tones when applied to SDXL 1.0 based Checkpoints.

LoKRs are specific kind of LoRAs that use some fancy math to keep their size very small (This is just 7MB, compared to 200-700MB sized LoRAs!)

What this does mean, though, is that:

  1. The LoKR may not translate to other checkpoints as well as the one it was trained on (or at all)

  2. The output may range from sublime to creepy, for the same prompt, based on how the AI influences your base checkpoint.

This was trained on SDXL 1.0, but seems to work best on the ZavyChromaXL checkpoint (https://civitai.com/models/119229/zavychromaxl)

Put this in your models>LoRA folder, and use it as you would use a LoRA.

Settings vary based on checkpoint, but very broadly:

CFG: 7-8

Steps: 20-40

Strength: 0.3-1

Sampler: euler a, DPM++ 2M SDE Karras

items.name: Make Noir | ComfyUI workflow
items.description:
An img2img workflow to convert any picture into monochrome noir style, accenting single color. Works with real life photos! (on some degree)

How it works

B&W filter + Cutoff = B&W picture with single detail colored.

Installation and dependencies

  1. Install WAS Node Suite custom nodes;

  2. Install Cutoff custom nodes;

  3. Download and open this workflow;

  4. (optional) Check "Resources and substitutions" section below for recommended extras.

Resources and substitutions

Complete list of all resources chosen in nodes:

LoRAs: Film Noir Style. It's recommended, but optional. How to substitute: shortcut the node and change text "(NoirStyle:1.2)" to "(monocrome, greyscale:0.5)" in "Trigger prefix" node.

EPI Noise Offset. It's recommended, but optional. How to substitute: just shortcut it.

SD model: Analog Madness. How to substitute: with any model.

VAEs: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned. Standard, recommended for encoding photos.

vae-ft-ema-560000-ema. Less details, recommended for decoding. How to substitute: use mse-840000.

items.name: Gradual Upscale | ComfyUI workflow
items.description:
A workflow for SD upscale without deformations or breaking initial composition too much.

How it works

Little upscale * little upscale * little upscale = Big upscale

Denoise is lowered each iteration.

Installation and dependencies

  1. Install WAS Node Suite custom nodes;

  2. Download and open this workflow;

  3. (optional) Check "Resources and substitutions" section below for recommended extras.

Resources and substitutions

Complete list of all resources chosen in nodes across versions:

VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned. Standard, recommended for more details.

Realistic:

SD models: epiCRealism. How to substitute: with any realistic model.

Analog Madness. How to substitute: with any photorealistic model.

Upscaler model: 4xNMKD Superscale. How to substitute: download 4xESRGAN (or take it from Automatic1111).

Textual Inversions: bad_prompt_version2. Lower the weight for unusual compositions.

Deep Negative. Use 16T for base generation, and 2T for upscale.

bad-Hands-5. Use with 0.8 weight.

How to substitute TIs: just skip.

Anime:

SD models: CamelliaMix. How to substitute: with any anime model.

OnlyAnime. How to substitute: with any anime model.

Upscale Model: 4xNMKD YandereNeo XL. How to substitute: download 4xUltraSharp.

Textual Inversions: EasyNegative. Recommended.

badhandv4. Only use if hands are not important. Otherwise use bad-Hands-5 (but it might change the whole picture).

How to substitute TIs: just skip.

Latent

There is a version using latent upscaler. It DO change composition.

Check out my other workflows

In this model, I wanted to achieve different results for my prompts. What I have obseved in SDXL models is my prompts are more or less very similar in results with the same settings, and seeds. I feel a new model/merge should have a fairly different result. So that was the aim of this merge. It uses random smooth curve algorithms on the blocks until I got results I liked for my prompts.

items.name: CuteCore
items.description:
This model has been fine-tuned on over 75k images of cute characters from a base of NAI on NVIDIA A100.

This model should not be used for NSFW purposes but if it is I will not be held responsible.

This model should not be used for further training as it contains data that no other model does and would break cross-compatibility.

This model has been tested for compatibility with character LoRAs trained from numerous other models successfully while retaining style.

This model has been tested for compatibility with concept LoRAs trained from numerous other models successfully.

This model has been tested for compatibility with style LoRAs trained from numerous other models with varying degrees of success, please use a lower weight.

Due to the training base this model works best with LoRAs created from NAI.

All previews are generated with only this base model - No LoRAs, no Textual Inversions, no Aesthetic Embeddings, no ControlNet. The only exception to this is the last preview which used a LoRA to show compatibility.

All previews are generated without negative prompts. All previews are generated at 512x704 with 2x hires fix. using the latest WebUI and 4x-UltraSharp upscaler.

Great care has been taken to ensure that previews are within the bounds of the rules and that there is ample description provided of what this is and how it was made and used. This model should not be eligible for deletion as all rules have been followed. If any previews are found to be NSFW in any way - please seek help, you need it.

The traits of this model include specifically cute and adorable looking with a focus on correct body composition without need for negative prompts. Heterochromia was specifically trained as well but is still random colors only. Negative prompts may still be used if needed. Hires fix. is recommended. The better your prompt the better the output.

This model may or may not be capable of creating older or more mature looking characters. It has been attempted for a short period of time with low success rate.

items.name: Snoodler | Use SD LoRa's with SDXL Models | Workflow
items.description:
Snoodler SDXL to SD LoRa Workflow

About

This is a simple workflow that helps you use SD 1.5 LoRa's with the new SDXL 1.0 models. Render your old SD LoRa's in 1024x1024 the easy way!

Are you frustrated that you cant use your old SD 1.5 LoRa with the new SDXL 1.0 models? Look no further! This workflow helps you render an image using the new SDXL 1.0 models in a 1024x1024 size or larger, then use that rendered image as a baseline for your SD 1.5 models and LoRa to change. This not only enhances your pictures by using the new SDXL 1.0 models for better detail and generation, but now your old LoRa will be rendered higher than the old 512x512 size.

Now you can use all those old futanari LoRa's you have collecting dust with SDXL 1024x1024 renders! 🤣

Usage Tips

This workflow uses the new text_g and text_l prompt technique. You can either research this or load this workflow and there is a brief explanation in a note node. I have also pre-filled the prompts so you can see the difference between the two and have an example to start with.

If you need to skip some refining steps, image save steps, upscaling steps, or load extra LoRa in the workflow, just use the bypass option that I explain in the notes node.

Depending on the LoRa you are trying to use, you will have to think about how your base image should be generated and prompted. Most style LoRa do all the work by themselves. If you have a very niche LoRa for example a coffee latte style LoRa, it might take some creative prompting to get the base image that will let your SD 1.5 models and LoRa complete the correct work.

Thank You!

Thanks for checking out my workflow! Please leave a like and rating if you try it and like what you see. I'm fairly new to ComfyUI and this whole AI generation, but if you have any feedback or questions feel free to post them and I'll help in any way I can.

items.name: 【再世】next life-李钰
items.description:
这是群星再世第七十五期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

李钰毕业于上海戏剧学院，与李冰冰、任泉是同班同学，出生于1976年12月20的她，在大二时因在《情深深雨漾蒙》中出演方瑜而备受好评，被誉为第六代“琼瑶女郎”。2002年李钰与邵兵合作悬疑剧《猎豹出击》，剧中饰演“容雨君”。2006年在《雾柳镇》中饰演戏班刀马旦名角“紫苏”，无论是温柔如水的女性还是心狠手辣的间谍，都被李钰演绎得淋漓尽致。随后李钰在电视剧《末代皇妃》中饰演川岛芳子，还主演过电影《怒江魂》和《恰同学少年》等多部作品。

李钰因为幽默开朗的性格，在学校以及校外表演的小节目都是千变万化的性格，因此在上海戏剧学院上学时还获得了一个外号“女版周星驰”，当时因为这点，黄晓明被她深深吸引，成为李钰在学校期间的男朋友，但俩人在一起的时间很短暂，后来李钰拍摄《猎豹出击》时和邵兵产生了感情，但俩人聚少离多，最终也没有结果。李钰拍起戏来是属于拼命三郎的状态，因此每次拍戏结束后，李钰就经常去夜店释放压力，久而久之身体出现了问题，李钰得了淋巴癌，在后来某一次剧集拍摄的庆功宴上，李钰碰上了汪雨，汪雨被李钰深深吸引，即使李钰告诉他自己身患淋巴癌，汪雨也没放弃追求，并且陪着李钰积极治疗，李钰生前交代自己想在去世的时候穿婚纱，汪雨也答应了这一请求，去世后的追悼会，汪雨也是以男友身份出现。

李钰，2009年因癌症去世，年仅32岁。

恰好，你是我喜欢的类型（我觉得她也是整个《情深深雨濛濛》里唯一三观还算正常的人。。。）
